Module jdk.management
Package com.ibm.lang.management

Interface GarbageCollectorMXBean

All Superinterfaces:
GarbageCollectorMXBean, GarbageCollectorMXBean, MemoryManagerMXBean, PlatformManagedObject
All Known Implementing Classes:
ExtendedGarbageCollectorMXBeanImpl
public interface GarbageCollectorMXBean extends GarbageCollectorMXBean
The OpenJ9 extension interface for managing and monitoring the virtual machine's garbage collection functionality.
Since:
1.5
